data.title: It is closed permanently
data.text: This venue is permanently closed. Too bad. Could have been a fun place to go that wasn't a bar. Not a lot of other options in downtown Midland after dark.

data.title: Unimpressed
data.text: We were unimpressed, but we're over 40.  The place is dark and dirty. The drinks were medium hot only and way too much foam for the price.  The couch and chair combo were very old and bug habitat looking.  These worn out furniture set would not even sell in a garage sale. The place might be a good hang out for teens.  We won't be back.
